# Placeholder so `crates/sorng-opkssh-vendor/bundle/opkssh/` exists in a clean
# checkout. tauri.conf.json declares this path in bundle.resources, and
# tauri-build validates its existence during `cargo check` (before the real
# `stage:opkssh-vendor --enable` step runs on `tauri build`). Without this the
# rust check jobs fail: "resource path ... doesn't exist". The real build
# overwrites this directory's contents via beforeBuildCommand.
